snippet.title: Fitness Boxing 2: Rhythm & Exercise - Announcement Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Pre-order Fitness Boxing 2 now: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/fitness-boxing-2-rhythm-and-exercise-switch/
Move to the beat with boxing exercises in Fitness Boxing 2: Rhythm & Exercise, coming to Nintendo Switch on 12/4! This sequel includes several new features like two-player mode, three new instructors, an alarm function, and more!

#FitnessBoxing2 #NintendoSwitch
